OL,3,CDUP to use Stormont's brake for the
OL,4,Cfirst time
OL,6,FThe Democratic Unionist Party (DUP) is
OL,7,Fintending to use the 'Stormont Brake'
OL,8,Fmechanism for the first time in an
OL,9,Fattempt to stop new EU rules on
OL,10,Fpackaging and labelling of chemicals
OL,11,Ffrom applying to NI.
OL,13,FThe brake, which was introduced as
OL,14,Fpart of Northern Ireland's Brexit deal
OL,15,Fand gives the Stormont assembly the
OL,16,Fpower to object to changes to EU rules
OL,17,Fthat apply in Northern Ireland.
