OL,3,CDUP to use Stormont's brake for the
OL,4,Cfirst time
OL,6,FThe decision comes after industry
OL,7,Frepresentatives warned that an updated
OL,8,FEU law affecting the labelling of
OL,9,Fchemicals would create additional
OL,10,Ftrade friction for the flow of
OL,11,Fproducts between Great Britain and
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,14,FTo pass the brake, 30 assembly members
OL,15,Ffrom at least two parties are needed
OL,16,Fto support it.
OL,18,FCurrently the DUP have 27 signatures.
