OL,6,FIf the number of votes required is
OL,7,Fmet, the UK government will decide if
OL,8,Fit has been used appropriately.
OL,10,FAs part of the judgement, it must
OL,11,Fprove to have "a significant impact
OL,12,Fspecific to every day life of
OL,13,Fcommunities in Northern Ireland" to be
OL,14,Fapproved.
OL,16,FParty Leader Rt Hon Gavin Robinson MP
OL,17,Fsaid: ''The DUP is focused on fully
OL,18,Frestoring Northern Ireland's place in
OL,19,Fthe United Kingdom and its internal
OL,20,Fmarket.
