OL,3,CDUP to use Stormont's brake for the
OL,4,Cfirst time
OL,6,F"We have made no secret of the fact
OL,7,Fthat we will use the Stormont Brake to
OL,8,Ffull effect in the pursuit of our
OL,9,Foverall objectives.
OL,11,F"This EU regulation introduces a host
OL,12,Fof new requirements for labels
OL,13,Fattached to chemical products,
OL,14,Fincluding new minimum font sizes and
OL,15,Frules around spacing.
OL,17,F"This would make current labels
OL,18,Funusable for the majority of products.
OL,19,FCritically, these changes would not be
OL,20,Frequired for products on the market in
OL,21,FGreat Britain.
