OL,6,F"With trade flows in chemicals between
OL,7,FGreat Britain and Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fworth in the region of #1bn annually,
OL,9,Fthe impact of this divergence would be
OL,10,Fsignificant.
OL,12,F"The Chemical Industries Association
OL,13,F(CIA), which represents chemical and
OL,14,Fpharmaceutical companies across the
OL,15,FUnited Kingdom, has assessed that the
OL,16,FRegulation would have a significant,
OL,17,Fnegative and prolonged impact on
OL,18,Feveryday life in Northern Ireland."
